race.comment: TACTFULL (3) has produced performances at two of his last three outings that stack up favourably in this company. Ran out of his skin in the Traralgon Cup three back then raced handy and was brave in finishing third over 1968m at Yarra Valley last start. Has his share of weight but looks the testing material. PIPLUP (14) ran a nice race first-up at Colac then found the mile too short at Cranbourne last time. Needs this trip at the third run back so watch for a far better performance. OUTCASTER (9) found some form last start at the fourth run of the campaign, making a sustained run to get up for second over 1968m at Yarra Valley. Nicely in after the claim and she has three top three finishes from four tries at this distance. Poses a serious threat. UNQUESTIONABLY (4) is in the mix coming back in grade at the fourth run in from a spell. JAKK'S FORTUNE (6) wasn't far away last start at Yarra Valley and will appreciate the step up in distance.
